| 1 |  | #P_ax-frege54c | |- x = x |
\
 Reflexive equality of sets.  The content of ` x ` is identical with the content of ` x ` .  Part of Axiom 54 of [Frege1879] p. 50.  Slightly specialized version of ~ eqid .  (Contributed by RP, 24-Dec-2019.) (Proof modification is discouraged.)
